-- P0-15 (both directions, regression): an attribute on a signature-less def
-- must NOT unbind it. Before the fix, resolve/typecheck/eval/ir top-level
-- collectors dropped the DAttrib-wrapped DFunDef → `Unbound variable: f` under
-- run/check and a build panic. All three engines must now ACCEPT and agree.
@inline
f x = x + 1

main = println (f 3)
